接口 ResponseHandlerInterface

  • 所有已知实现类:

    public interface ResponseHandlerInterface
    Interface to standardize implementations

      • sendFailureMessage

                      Header[] headers,
                      byte[] responseBody,

        参数:

        headers - returned headers
        responseBody - returned data
        error - cause of request failure

      • setUseSynchronousMode

        void setUseSynchronousMode(boolean useSynchronousMode)
        Can set, whether the handler should be asynchronous or synchronous
        参数:

      • getUseSynchronousMode

        boolean getUseSynchronousMode()
        Returns whether the handler is asynchronous or synchronous
        返回:
        boolean if the ResponseHandler is running in synchronous mode

      • onPreProcessResponse

        void onPreProcessResponse(ResponseHandlerInterface instance,
                        HttpResponse response)
        This method is called once by the system when the response is about to be processed by the system. The library makes sure that a single response is pre-processed only once. Please note: pre-processing does NOT run on the main thread, and thus any UI activities that you must perform should be properly dispatched to the app's UI thread.
        参数:
        instance - An instance of this response object
        response - The response to pre-processed

      • onPostProcessResponse

        void onPostProcessResponse(ResponseHandlerInterface instance,
                         HttpResponse response)
        This method is called once by the system when the request has been fully sent, handled and finished. The library makes sure that a single response is post-processed only once. Please note: post-processing does NOT run on the main thread, and thus any UI activities that you must perform should be properly dispatched to the app's UI thread.
        参数:
        instance - An instance of this response object
        response - The response to post-process
